  ('73d36f84-e6a7-4e74-aa62-bacaf1ced86a', 'MT.2.NS.NP.3', 'Use a variety of tools (such as counters, pictures, number lines and drawings) to generate and interpret whole number sequences involving doubling', 'mathematics', '2', 'Number Sense', 'NS', 'Number Patterns', 'NP', '', 'K-2', 3, '2026-01-03T13:23:37.075008+00:00', '2026-01-03T13:23:37.075008+00:00'),
