  ('4d174301-9b62-4320-876b-f0ff750f0025', 'MT.2.NS.OS.5', 'Interpret repeated addition (multiplication) procedures, using terms (such as ''sets of'', ''times'', ''groups of'')', 'mathematics', '2', 'Number Sense', 'NS', 'Operational Sense', 'OS', '', 'K-2', 5, '2026-01-03T13:23:37.075008+00:00', '2026-01-03T13:23:37.075008+00:00'),
